testsuite.name: testng.tessco.Registration
testsuite.system-out:
1. Launch the home page



2. Login and Register page


3. Registration page


4. User able to select New Registration Button


5. User able to Enter Company legal entity name, country, Company Billing Address Line 1 and Company Billing Address Line 2


6. User able to enter City, postal code, AP first name, AP last name, AP email and AP phone


7. User able to enter First name, Last name, email, Phone, Tessco.com username, password and confirm password


7. User able to register successfully
